Class CellListUtilization

Object
CellListUtilization
public class CellListUtilization
extends Object
This class contains the main method which utilizes the CellPhone and CellList classes. This program's purpose is practice LinkedList concept theory. It reads from a text file with multiple cell phone information, then puts them into CellPhone objects which are added into a linked list. From this linked list, many of its methods are tested. Concepts: LinkedList data structure; creating a linked list, nodes/references and its methods + File I/O; reading data from text file into objects.
